<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF606ADFF7ED9EFF1760B149" pageId="155" pageNumber="916" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF606ADFF7ED9EFF1760B149" blockId="155.[2064,2659,2135,2562]" lastBlockId="155.[1452,2660,2579,3473]" pageId="155" pageNumber="916">
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF606ADFF7ED9EFF16F5B3F5" baseAuthorityName="Scully" baseAuthorityYear="1881" box="[2065,2293,2214,2247]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="155" pageNumber="916" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tubinaris">Murina tubinaris</taxonomicName>
previously included populations that are now attributed to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF606ADFF5F89E941463B3DC" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1891" box="[2564,2659,2253,2286]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Harpiocephalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="155" pageNumber="916" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="feae">M. feae</taxonomicName>
(including 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF606ADFF7499EAD175BB227" authorityName="Csorba &amp; Furey" authorityYear="2011" box="[2229,2395,2292,2325]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="155" pageNumber="916" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="cineracea">M. cineracea</taxonomicName>
as a synonym) in Indochina, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF606ADFF7419F7D1762B20F" box="[2237,2402,2340,2365]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="155" pageNumber="915" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beelzebub">M. beelzebub</taxonomicName>
in central Annamite Mountains, and M. jaintianainJaintia Hills of 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF606ADFF77F9F3216CCB2BE" box="[2179,2252,2411,2444]" name="India" pageId="155" pageNumber="916">India</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF606ADFF6EA9F321759B2BE" box="[2326,2393,2411,2444]" country="Myanmar" name="Chin" pageId="155" pageNumber="916">Chin</collectingRegion>
Hills of 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF606ADFF62B9F32145CB2BE" box="[2519,2652,2411,2444]" name="Myanmar" pageId="155" pageNumber="916">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
. Genetic and morphological data restricted 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF606ADFF7C29FE316E0B2E9" baseAuthorityName="Scully" baseAuthorityYear="1881" box="[2110,2272,2490,2523]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="155" pageNumber="11" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tubinaris">M. tubinaris</taxonomicName>
to north-western 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF606ADFF6269FE31424B2E9" box="[2522,2596,2490,2523]" name="India" pageId="155" pageNumber="916">India</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF606ADFF7EE9FB81689B130" box="[2066,2185,2529,2562]" name="Pakistan" pageId="155" pageNumber="916">Pakistan</collectingCountry>
. Specific status of specimens from West Bengal, Arunachal Pradesh, Mizoram, Sikkim, and some areas of northern 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF606ADFF5F29C4A1BE6B160" name="Myanmar" pageId="155" pageNumber="916">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
that were previously included under 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF606ADFF8139C681690B160" baseAuthorityName="Scully" baseAuthorityYear="1881" box="[2031,2192,2609,2642]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="155" pageNumber="11" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tubinaris">M. tubinaris</taxonomicName>
and distributional limits between cryptic speciessplit from 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF606ADFF8EE9C0319B4B149" baseAuthorityName="Scully" baseAuthorityYear="1881" box="[1810,1972,2650,2683]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="155" pageNumber="11" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tubinaris">M. tubinaris</taxonomicName>
remain uncertain. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
